      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The engine struggles to start and runs roughly, while the transmission exhibits significant slipping and delay when shifting. Cosmetically, the car shows its age with extensive rust on the body panels, faded paint, and a heavily worn interior with several tears in the upholstery. This would be an ideal candidate for a complete restoration project or for someone looking for a source of spare parts, as it requires substantial mechanical and body work to be roadworthy again.",
