      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, currently held in a state of pristine preservation. This unit exhibits the highest standards of automotive care, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in showroom condition. Mechanically uncompromising and meticulously maintained, this vehicle offers a peerless driving experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast. It represents a rare opportunity to acquire a top-tier asset that transcends the typical secondary market offering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
